705732f-a.title: Brooklyn: Mill Street - Henry Street
705732f-a.text:
Mill Street, east from Henry to Clinton Streets. This and
surrounding areas are to be demolished. The Red Hook Housing
Project has taken over the area to erect low rent multiple dwellings
thereby slowly removing the slum areas of Greater New York.
June 9, 1938.
P. L. Sperr
NO RFPRODUCTIONS.
